Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:07.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}终于找到了  全新的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:11.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}日月却来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:16.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}我前往的地方  不是“未来”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:20.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仅仅不停地追赶着“过去”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:26.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}不停地鸣响着 那过去的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:31.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仿佛无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:36.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}差不多了吧  那厌倦搜索的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:41.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}丢掉心里的纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:46.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  总有会停的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:52.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这么漫长  却如此冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  为什么会选择我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:02.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}笼罩着我  真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:06.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  已经忘了停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:12.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天依然持续下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:17.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在默默撑开的雨伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:28.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}接近那温暖的怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:41.79,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}从那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:46.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}就决定不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:51.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}即使承担再多的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:56.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仍有无法原谅的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:00.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经无法回到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:02.65,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:07.74,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还没有做成任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:12.99,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的记忆之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:18.87,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}又有一块  消逝而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:21.88,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回望今日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:24.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:29.76,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}期望这个声音总有一天可以传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:32.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:34.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在风停止的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:39.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仰望天空追寻着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:46.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}在黎明前散发的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:52.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}将会变成彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要…进行人体炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会做的吧 马斯坦古君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会进行人体炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要舍弃吗 真冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍弃？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这些人当弃子一样使唤的你没资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是弃子 他们也很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些被父母抛弃 放任不管就会死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给他们带来了食物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带来了一流的教育
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后给予了他们存在的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都很感谢我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为这样 你才会马失前蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们确实很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为能把你抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点放了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现…现在能使用炼金术的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我那个女人就没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连说的话都是三流的 医生大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:03:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睁开眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有那个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边优先
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 先止血了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后要好好给医生看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说话 休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你察觉到我的眼神了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在一起很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果进行人体炼成就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用这种眼神告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 对不住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有什么 小事一桩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金格·布拉德雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口没有再生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了 马斯坦古君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别来无恙 好像不能这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德雷 死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本以为是你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面前有重要的人倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会毫不犹豫地进行人体炼成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的我 也许会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在有阻止我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有给我指明正确道路的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为人类是永远不会学习的可怜生物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有像你们这样在短时间内学习并变化的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 人类这种生物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能如我所愿 真让人生气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:07:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在正下方很深的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你们妨碍那位大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃吧 老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰尔森？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么恐怖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 中尉就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我培养的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是第五人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是最后一人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么今天这么爱闹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太想用这招的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要强行让你开门了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人体炼成什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你没有这个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人体炼成知识的炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经和普莱德同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他拥有构筑式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开 拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你会被拿走哪一部分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 会被卷进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人体炼成完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚才的眼镜老头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:11:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马斯坦古君在父亲大人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是完好无损就不能保证了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 现在我是如你所见的这副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒亚美斯多利斯大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名扬天下的会是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是合成兽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是外人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是马斯坦古的忠犬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员一起上呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对着一个全身是伤的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有能赢的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正下方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个洞的下方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅说了在正下方之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼镜老头就动摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说“不会让你们妨碍那位大人”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是不想让我们去下面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是中心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正下方有很强的气之集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是第五人 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}（没事吧？大佐）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五人到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}（振作点 大佐）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是阿尔冯斯·艾尔利克没到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幕后主谋所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐 到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在全白的空间里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从非常大的门里出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 有什么被拿走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手 脚都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这黑暗之中 你还能看到我的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片黑 什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难 难道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛看不到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的国家炼金术师之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的能力是最麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那里绝望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了人体炼成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我会做那种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是强行让他打开门的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达到目的就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样最麻烦的马斯坦古大佐的战斗力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和零一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理很残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有自知之明 就想让死人复活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追求母亲温暖的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:16:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被拿走了支撑身体的脚和唯一的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个人全身被拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了无法感觉温暖的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追求失去的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果变成了永远无法得到孩子的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 看透国家未来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视力被拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再看未来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了使人类不自傲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给予正确的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那正是你们人类称为神的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我们这样 自己做的我可以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强迫完全不想做的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行人体炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被拿走视力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那能叫正确吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种不正确的真理我不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想妨碍父亲大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真正的名字是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是巧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道自己的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同是无名人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:18:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相互厮杀也挺有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在我家开洞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外表虽然变了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那气息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是长生不老的主谋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他醒不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:18:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这细小的手臂是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有骨头和皮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能站着就已经是全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能用这种身体战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家明明都在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想和我合为一体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一直想着要恢复原来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种身体不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种身体不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想回到那边？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想用那个身体回到那边？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去的话 我不会阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再努力一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了救同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把常年寻找的肉体丢下了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.08,0:22:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那高洁的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作为你的容器而感到骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.07,0:22:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会因为你回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而使这个世界充满绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凑齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,勇气被力量所压倒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福被击得粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.46,0:24:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.98,0:24:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第60话 天之瞳 地之门
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界已被黑暗包围了
